decks.notes: The deck focuses on quickly deploying aggressive Spirit creatures and protecting them with counter spells and evasion abilities. By building a board presence early and continuously applying pressure, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent before they can stabilize. The combination of low-cost creatures with powerful anthems like Supreme Phantom and efficient card draw from Curious Obsession allows the deck to maintain momentum and threaten the opponent's life total. The inclusion of utility lands like Faceless Haven and Otawara, Soaring City provide additional versatility and threats to close out the game.

This deck focuses on aggressively attacking the opponent with creatures like Bloodtithe Harvester and Bonecrusher Giant, while disrupting their hand with cards like Thoughtseize and Power Word Kill. Kroxa, Titan of Death's Hunger and Sheoldred, the Apocalypse provide additional threats to pressure the opponent. Misery's Shadow and Graveyard Trespasser help to control the opponent's resources. The deck also includes removal spells like Fatal Push and Dreadbore to deal with opposing threats. The mana base supports the deck's aggressive plan with a mix of dual lands and utility lands.
